__END__

=head1 Title

  Test IKEv2.SGW.R.1.1.6.5: Receiving Multiple Transforms for CHILD_SA
  Part A: Multiple Encryption Algorithms (BASIC)

=head1 Purpose

  To verify an IKEv2 device properly handles IKE_SA_INIT request with an unacceptable SA
  payload.

=head1 References

  * [RFC 4306] - Sections 3.3

=head1 Test Setup

  * Network Topology
      Connect the devices according to the Common Topology.
  * Configuration
      In each part, configure the devices according to the Common Configuration.
  * Pre-Sequence and Cleanup Sequence
      IKEv2 on the NUT is disabled after each part.

